# Install

    $ pip install linux-touchpad


# Usage


## Start

To begin the process, use this command:

    $ python -m linux_touchpad start


## Toggle

Enabled the touchpad and ignore mouse events:

    $ python -m linux_touchpad toggle


## Stop

    $ python -m linux_touchpad stop


